      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Twilit Twin Stars",
        "Client": "Convalescing Hunter",
        "Description": "It was a quiet night in the Ruins;\r\nthat\u0027s when I saw two red stars\r\nglowing in the darkness. I felt a\r\ngust of wind, and the next thing\r\nI knew, I awoke on a hospital bed.\r\nI did not know such frightening\r\nthings exist out there...",
        "Target": "Hunt a Nargacuga",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "\u00C9toiles jumelles",
        "Client": "Chasseur convalescent",
        "Description": "Tout \u00E9tait calme au Temple, et tout\r\n\u00E0 coup, j\u0027ai vu deux \u00E9toiles rouges\r\ndans le noir. J\u0027ai senti un coup de\r\nvent et tout ce dont je me souviens,\r\nc\u0027est d\u0027\u00EAtre \u00E0 l\u0027h\u00F4pital. J\u0027aurais\r\njamais imagin\u00E9 qu\u0027un truc aussi\r\neffrayant puisse exister...",
        "Target": "Chasser un Nargacuga",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Stelle del crepuscolo",
        "Client": "Cacciatore convalescente",
        "Description": "Era una notte tranquilla alle\r\nrovine, ma poi ho visto due\r\nstelle rosse nel buio. Ho\r\nsentito una folata di vento e\r\nmi sono risvegliato dritto in\r\nospedale. Che esseri tremendi,\r\nnon pensavo che esistessero!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Nargacuga",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Zwillingssterne im Zwielicht",
        "Client": "Genesender J\u00E4ger",
        "Description": "Es war eine ruhige Nacht in den\r\nRuinen, aber zwei Lichter haben\r\nwie Sterne im Dunkeln gefunkelt.\r\nIch habe einen Windsto\u00DF gesp\u00FCrt,\r\nund meine n\u00E4chste Erinnerung ist\r\naus dem Krankenhausbett. Dass\r\nes da so furchtbare Dinge gibt...",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Nargacuga.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Astros gemelos en el ocaso",
        "Client": "Cazador convaleciente",
        "Description": "Una tranquila noche en el\r\ntemplo vi dos estrellas rojas.\r\nSe esfumaron antes de que\r\npudiese reaccionar; sent\u00ED una\r\nr\u00E1faga de viento y me despert\u00E9\r\nen el hospital. \u00A1Esa cosa no\r\npuede campar a sus anchas!",
        "Target": "Caza un Nargacuga",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0414\u0432\u0435 \u0437\u0432\u0435\u0437\u0434\u044B",
